Fhjull Forked-Tongue
A victim of Trias, whom he calls "the Betrayer." He signed a
contract with the Deva that consigned him to acts of charity until
Trias is dead. He makes his home in the bones of Ul-Goris in the
Outlands, hiding from mortal and immortal alike. He has knowledge and
items that may prove useful.
